---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="VisionCable Supply was founded by embedded systems engineers to bring technical expertise to industrial cable sourcing."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge" data-i18n="about.badge">Our Story</span>
      <h1 data-i18n="about.title">Engineer-Founded. Quality-Driven.</h1>
      <p data-i18n="about.desc">We started VisionCable because we saw a gap: robotics companies needed cables, but cable suppliers did not understand the engineering behind them.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-content">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2 data-i18n="about.whyStarted">Why We Started</h2>
          <p>
            After years working in embedded systems, camera pipelines, and automotive electronics,
            we noticed the same problem over and over: engineers and procurement teams spending
            weeks trying to find the right cable, only to receive products with incorrect
            specifications or poor shielding.
          </p>
          <p>
            Most cable suppliers on B2B platforms copy-paste generic descriptions and cannot
            answer basic technical questions. They forward every inquiry to a factory and wait days
            for a response. For a robotics engineer trying to ship a product, this is frustrating
            and expensive.
          </p>
          <p>
            We built VisionCable to be different. When you ask about MIPI lane configuration,
            shielding coverage percentages, or M12 coding types, you are talking to someone who
            actually understands signal integrity and connector specifications.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-values">
          <div class="value-card card">
            <div class="value-icon">01</div>
            <h3 data-i18n="about.values.tech">Technical Expertise</h3>
            <p data-i18n="about.values.techDesc">We understand MIPI CSI-2, GMSL, FPD-Link, M12 coding, signal integrity, and shielding requirements. You get accurate answers, not guesswork.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card">
            <div class="value-icon">02</div>
            <h3 data-i18n="about.values.honest">Honest Specifications</h3>
            <p data-i18n="about.values.honestDesc">We publish full specifications: AWG, impedance, shielding coverage, temperature range. No vague descriptions or hidden details.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card">
            <div class="value-icon">03</div>
            <h3 data-i18n="about.values.direct">Direct Communication</h3>
            <p data-i18n="about.values.directDesc">No layers of sales reps between you and the answer. Ask a technical question, get a technical answer within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card">
            <div class="value-icon">04</div>
            <h3 data-i18n="about.values.verified">Verified Quality</h3>
            <p data-i18n="about.values.verifiedDesc">Every cable is continuity-tested and visually inspected before shipping. We do not ship untested products, period.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="location-card card">
        <h2 data-i18n="about.locationTitle">Based in Shenzhen, China</h2>
        <p data-i18n="about.locationDesc">
          We are located in Shenzhen, the world's electronics manufacturing hub. This gives us
          direct access to connector manufacturers, cable assembly factories, and component
          suppliers throughout the Pearl River Delta region.
        </p>
        <div class="location-features">
          <div class="loc-feature">
            <strong data-i18n="about.feature1.title">Direct Factory Access</strong>
            <p data-i18n="about.feature1.desc">Skip the trading company markup. We work directly with ISO-certified manufacturers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="loc-feature">
            <strong data-i18n="about.feature2.title">Fast Prototyping</strong>
            <p data-i18n="about.feature2.desc">Sample cables typically ready in 5-7 working days.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="loc-feature">
            <strong data-i18n="about.feature3.title">Quality Control</strong>
            <p data-i18n="about.feature3.desc">On-site inspection and testing before any shipment leaves.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.page-header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f5ff 0%, #e8f4f8 100%);
  padding: 60px 0 48px;
  text-align: center;
}

.page-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.4rem;
  margin: 16px 0 12px;
}

.page-header p {
  color: var(--color-text-light);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.about-content {
  max-width: 960px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  margin-bottom: 64px;
}

.about-text h2 {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.about-text p {
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.about-values {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
}

.value-card {
  padding: 24px;
}

.value-icon {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-accent);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.value-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.value-card p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-light);
}

.location-card {
  padding: 40px;
  background: var(--color-bg-alt);
}

.location-card h2 {
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.location-card > p {
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.location-features {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
}

.loc-feature strong {
  display: block;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.loc-feature p {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-light);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .about-values { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 1.7rem; }
}
</style>
